  "keyFeatures": [
    "Web-based game server management panel with Vue frontend",
    "REST API for programmatic control of game servers",
    "Multi-node architecture with lightweight daemon agents (GameAP Daemon)",
    "Support for PostgreSQL, MySQL/MariaDB, and SQLite databases",
    "Role-based access control (RBAC) for granular permissions",
    "WebAssembly plugin system for extending functionality",
    "Built-in file manager for server file operations",
    "Scheduled server tasks (cron-style automation)",
    "RCON support for in-game commands and player management",
    "TLS/HTTPS support with certificate management",
    "Redis and in-memory caching with configurable TTLs",
    "Local and S3-compatible file storage backends",
    "Personal Access Tokens (PAT) with scoped abilities",
    "Import games from Pelican egg format",
    "Docker-first deployment with multi-platform images"
  ],
